rows.label: qst702005_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh...?
Hey, you're the guys from before!

rows.label: qst702005_msg0002
rows.name:
We got chased around by some Tirkins,
and we ended up here...

rows.label: qst702005_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm glad we found you.
Though it did take us a while...

rows.label: qst702005_msg0005
rows.name:
Since our Da didn't seem to be coming,
and living the camp life with just the
two of us was getting too hard...

rows.label: qst702005_msg0006
rows.name:
We thought, next time we run into you
guys, we'd ask you to take us with you
to Superbia!

rows.label: qst702005_msg0007
rows.name:
I guess we could've left some notes in
the camp or in Torigo for Da to find,
but...

rows.label: qst702005_msg0008
rows.name:
For all I know, he might be dead...
And dead folks aren't great at reading...

rows.label: qst702005_msg0009
rows.name:
...Oh come on!
I'm pouring my heart out to you here!
What're you smirking for?!

rows.label: qst702005_msg0010
rows.name: What, follow you and I'll see?
